dct_title_s: Map shewing lines of railways in South Australia, 1887
dct_description_sm: Legend shows railways (including in construction and "for which bills have been passed"), stations.
Inset map: "Adelaide district enlarged : Scale. 8 Miles - 1 Inch."
Does not cover area west of Ceduna, South Australia.
